@node description "What is MoreText?"

MoreText is a powerful, yet easy to use text/AmigaGuide/HTML viewer.
It uses standard IO, so it's ideal for BBS usage. Of course it works
fine on shell too.

Viewing of AmigaGuides/HTML docs is very easy : use TAB to move to the next
link and RETURN to jump to a new node or file. Link jumps can be naturally
retraced. Also INDEX node is supported.

MoreText supports XPK system (crypting algorithms too) with all three
formats.

Other features include fast search and line jump routines etc...

@endnode

